'''鮑魚菇'''（[[學名|學名]]：{{lang|la|''Pleurotus cystidiosus''}}），常見的食用菇，屬於[[傘菌目|傘菌目]]下的[[側耳科|側耳科]]。
==分類==

鮑魚菇，又名泡囊側耳，與蠔菇([[平菇|平菇]])、[[杏鮑菇|杏鮑菇]]同屬[[側耳屬|側耳屬]]
同物異名:''[[Pleurotus|Pleurotus]] abalonus'' Y.H. Han, K.M. Chen & S. Cheng 1974 (synonym)、''[[Antromycopsis|Antromycopsis]] macrocarpa'' (Ellis & Everh.) Stalpers, Seifert & Samson 1991 (synonym).<ref>{{cite web|title=Pleurotus cystidiosus O.K. Miller 泡囊側耳 《臺灣生物多樣性資訊網-TaiBIF》|url=http://taibif.tw/zh/namecode/143290|access-date=2018-07-03|archive-date=2018-07-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180703133310/http://taibif.tw/zh/namecode/143290|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==型態==
鮑魚菇的菌柄側生或無菌柄，菌褶延伸至菌柄，孢子為白色。<ref>{{cite web |url= http://web2.nmns.edu.tw/fungi/Module/Module.php?Module=C01&Fungi_ID=34&show=1&Class_ID=9&Level2_ID=72&Level1_ID=17&cookie=del_L4 |title= 主題版真菌百科:鮑魚菇 |3=  |access-date= 2009-04-02 |archive-date= 2016-03-04 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20160304190932/http://web2.nmns.edu.tw/fungi/Module/Module.php?Module=C01&Fungi_ID=34&show=1&Class_ID=9&Level2_ID=72&Level1_ID=17&cookie=del_L4 |dead-url= no }}</ref>

==生態==
[[側耳屬|側耳屬]]的菇類常出現在[[熱帶氣候|熱帶氣候]]和[[溫帶氣候|溫帶氣候]]。<ref>{{cite book| title=Mushrooms: cultivation, nutritional value, medicinal effect, and environmental impact| first=Shu-ting| chapter=''Pleurotus'' – A Mushroom of Broad Adaptability| last=Chang| first2=Philip G.| last2=Miles| publisher=CRC Press| year=2004| pages=315–325| url=https://books.google.com/books?id=XO4EGzpp1M0C| isbn=978-0-8493-1043-0| edition=2nd}}</ref>而鮑魚菇[[子實體|子實體]]平均重量為25.4g，最佳生長溫度為25~28℃，子實體生長發育適宜的溫度為25~30℃，低於20℃和高於35℃子實體不發生，子實體長度能長到7.6~9.8cm。<ref>{{cite web |url= https://www.researchgate.net/publication/263623729_Studies_on_the_Morphological_and_Physiological_Characteristics_of_Pleurotus_cystidiosus_OKMiller_the_Abalone_Mushroom |title= Studies on the Morphological and Physiological Characteristics of Pleurotus cystidiosus O.K.Miller, the Abalone Mushroom |3=  |access-date= 2018-07-03 |archive-date= 2018-07-03 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20180703133343/https://www.researchgate.net/publication/263623729_Studies_on_the_Morphological_and_Physiological_Characteristics_of_Pleurotus_cystidiosus_OKMiller_the_Abalone_Mushroom |dead-url= no }}</ref>

